Healed dude brows!🧚‍♀️ This fella had very rounded features...round forehead...round nose..and sparse brows which left his eye area looking tiny which in turn made his jaw look small. We balanced the round features by giving him very angular brows with a strong arch(which mitigatesthe roundness). And made his jaw look much stronger by making his eyebrows long (this increases his total eye area which in turn makes his jaw look wider). We were beyond pleased with the results! What do you think?😁🤗
.
Microblader tip: I used tina davies in medium...microbladed strokes with zusing 16 from Amazon and shading with a 1 rl. I find stippling works better on male skin because it is much tougher. It takes longer, but the results are worth it!
.
